{
  "stem": "27390.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As we came into the street, the streets were deserted of people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was nobody about except every few yards there was a soldier with a machine gun.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they escorted us all the way.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And all the way-- and on the way, they knocked everything down.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Whatever we managed to carry with us, they knocked it out of our hands.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this went on till we finally reached the part where the ghetto was going to be.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "When we reached the ghetto-- it wasn't cordoned off of anything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was just we knew the streets, according to the plan that we saw in the paper, that there was going to be the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "For the first time, I saw Jewish police.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They didn't have uniforms.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They just had an armband with a Star of David on it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we were told, this is the Jewish police.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they handed us over to the Jewish-- the Gestapo, the SS handed us over to the Jewish police.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we were taken to a school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we were put into the school there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we stayed in the school for about two hours in the middle of the night.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was already late.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they announced-- the Jewish police announced that whoever has relations living in the ghetto can go to join up with the relations.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And whoever hasn't should stay in the school till they allotted some place where to live.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So we had an uncle living not far from there, so we went along there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And in the middle of the night-- they were all asleep-- we banged on the door.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They opened the door.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We came in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We told them what happened, and we all started crying.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
